{"tid":1664505,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳光誠是一個出生於山東沂南的盲人！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-20T07:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T16:28:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b15695cf3a6ab3f4b21df84835ae41b631538c","tid":1664505,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:21:50.000Z","msg":"雖然是很多人知道的事，但每次看到還是心潮澎湃。<br />\n<br />\n陳光誠是一個出生於山東沂南的盲人，他發現村民常因為缺乏法律知識而飽受欺凌，當地政府帶頭違法的情況普遍而蠻橫，他決定自學法律自救並幫鄰人抗爭，當村民們的法律顧問，下場是入獄四年，而出獄後被中國政府軟禁在家整整兩年，期間所有試圖要幫助他們一家的外媒、公益團體全遭受毆打跟凌辱。<br />\n<br />\n當時在中國拍片的Christian Bale聽聞他的事蹟決定私下去探望他，卻被中國官方安排好的民眾毆打。中國曾有過蝙蝠俠，而中國人的選擇是毆打他們。<br />\n<br />\n陳光誠2012年在各方協助下離開中國，同年度在美國並獲得人權至上獎Human Rights Award，頒獎人就是Christian Bale。"},{"pid":"96d35431c52e8da5832aa1dc318e47366ae85716","tid":1664505,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:29:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/shinmankanalbert/permalink/2037637553005499?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fshinmankanalbert%2Fpermalink%2F2037637553005499%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc8ZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=7e566765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/shinmankanalbert/permalink/2037637553005499?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"44e3c1d8147b03bbe60b2e1a942fe1ab398511e4","tid":1664505,"uid":79117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"中國真係一個劣幣驅逐良幣既國家。"},{"pid":"55da06f7972a30578a1e94a3d8240889e4173892","tid":1664505,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"Off topic<br />\n應該係...<br />\n中國曾有過「夜魔俠」"},{"pid":"66d29437a8819a168ce7d273b360f7af81a4366b","tid":1664505,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\